text: Alexandra Malzer also referred to as 'Malzer' (born 18 August 2000) is an English international field hockey player who plays as a forward for England and Great Britain. She plays club hockey in the British Universities and Colleges Sport (BUCS) league for University of Nottingham. Alex previously represented the England U16 and U18 national side winning a European bronze with the U18 team in the summer of 2018.
